  "original_title": "\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb5\u0b9a\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc8 \u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8\u0baf\u0bbe\u0b95 \u0b85\u0ba3\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0b8f\u0bb1\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd\u0bb3 \u0b86\u0baa\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Dangers of not wearing face masks properly",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Medical Officer Vasan Ratnasingham, member of the Central Committee and Media Committee of the Government Medical Officers Association, said that respiratory diseases are increasing due to improper wearing of face masks.",
        "Vasan Ratnasingham said that the public should follow the Covid-19 regulations properly and stay safe from respiratory problems. (R("
